escription><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5cLBFMQ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Same old same old: too much work, long hours, pay no up to par, got 5mo child at home. Decided to change scenery and profession alltogether. Been planning to quit for months but wife had no job so I couldn't leave us on nothing. Feels like I've been burning the candle from both ends, and there is not much to personal life since I feel a bit burnout creeping up. House needs fixing, kid needs attention and wife needs a husband, but after workday I'm too exhausted to do anything. Weekends go in a blur, and joy has left my life.

Finally yesterday she got a job and starts in two months. Figured I could leave my letter of resignation with 2 months notice and be stay-at-home dad for a while. Broke my ankle last September so my foot could use the downtime.

I printed two copies and signed them, figured I'd give em to boss after the day is done. Suddenly coworker stated at coffee break with a bang that he quits and our boss can shove it. "This is April Fool's, right?" 'NOPE, I'LL GET MY SHIT NEXT MONDAY!' Uses all his vacation days and left doors banging.

Boss is furious. So much work to do, nobody to do them. The position he left is almost the same as mine.

I'm bit afraid to walk in his office in 4 hours to tell him I doing the same thing. Wish me luck Imgurites!

MV EDIT: It's done. Walked to bosses office and handed him the papers. "Are you fucking kidding me??". Told him that I was going to take time for myself and my family. Got offered whopping 0,6% payraise, I told him that this wasn't about the money, I could almost see the ??? above his head. "Let's talk this through Monday, aight?" Sure, I'm still employed here for two months, but my mind is made up. If I have to choose between work and family, family wins 100 times out of 100.

He sighed and signed the papers. Gotta make documentation of my work for some poor bastard to take over after I'm gone. I work at multimillion process-automation company, so finding replacement for me shouldn't be too hard.

Thank you all for your kind words! I haven't felt this happy in 2 years. I'll celebrate with a nice pizza pie tonight! Stay safe!

EDIT2: Office Manager landed on my desk as I was packing and said "You should think before making these kind of tasteless April Fool's declarations. *Boss' name* is really furious", with a doubtful grin. I told him I was dead serious, and this was in no way a April Fool's. "Naaah, this is a joke, you're joking. We got lots of work orders to deliver". Welp, see if it's April Fool's at monday. 

I was thinking ordering deep dish pizza, haven't had one of those in a while. PHIIS!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/JAn7ckT</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Grindwinder]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>The best guard dog ever :D</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/vFFTJCg</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RO6dDLL.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Source : https://instagram.com/kelly_bove</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/vFFTJCg</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Rammsteinstochter]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Workers united, never be divided!!!!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/jr8CmKQ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8orOOLH.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/jr8CmKQ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mehbin]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>How I walk in shallow water</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/HtqgWCO</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4NAaxQj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/HtqgWCO</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mfrybeasley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Me when I see a new imgur April Fools Day gimmick:</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Lt9Yiwa</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Qahf1U2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Meh.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Lt9Yiwa</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[IntrovertedGiant]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Origins</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/k3b9bf8</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VdtBoJn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com